    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The lands of Ascrabeth are under threat and an alliance of the willing is gathering. You are responsible for providing your followers with everything they need to succeed! From crafting weapons to farming crops, you will do whatever is necessary to equip them with the finest gear, the tastiest provisions, and the most comfortable accommodations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/75ab45dee70485c4e433d96d840edca3.poster.avif?t=1770629050\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/75ab45dee70485c4e433d96d840edca3.webm?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/75ab45dee70485c4e433d96d840edca3.mp4?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft, Farm and Build</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your skills in gathering resources and crafting a wide range of hero-equipment. Cultivate a variety of crops to create delicious provisions and build up comfortable houses to furnish them cozily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/5e65f04b317a7bbf0497f43cd073ee3b.poster.avif?t=1770629050\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/5e65f04b317a7bbf0497f43cd073ee3b.webm?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/5e65f04b317a7bbf0497f43cd073ee3b.mp4?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lead your Heroes to Success</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your heroes, plan their missions, and assemble the most powerful teams for each adventure. Fulfill their individual needs to boost their morale and help them grow into the ultimate defenders of Ascrabeth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/42e0925c24a86714ffbee217363fb659.poster.avif?t=1770629050\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/42e0925c24a86714ffbee217363fb659.webm?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/42e0925c24a86714ffbee217363fb659.mp4?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Establish a Flourishing Village</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow the Fellowship of the Oak from a lone tavern into a thriving village where your heroes feel truly at home! As your fellowship grows, use workers to automate tasks in order to help you provide the best care for all of your residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/2f53e498b67a52a8bcafc1c4b73c1da5.poster.avif?t=1770629050\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/2f53e498b67a52a8bcafc1c4b73c1da5.webm?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/2f53e498b67a52a8bcafc1c4b73c1da5.mp4?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Fellowship</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fellowship of the Oak is developed by a small team of two  developers. We are open to feedback and welcome everyone who wishes to contribute ideas, suggestions and criticism :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/6a10548b08dcbe1f99434952b6d85b94.poster.avif?t=1770629050\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/6a10548b08dcbe1f99434952b6d85b94.webm?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207620/extras/6a10548b08dcbe1f99434952b6d85b94.mp4?t=1770629050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
